query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(it1 it2 k mi mi_idx mk t kt) */ select min(mi_idx.info) AS rating,
min(t.title) AS north_european_dark_production
from keyword AS k
inner join movie_keyword AS mk
on k.id = mk.keyword_id AND k.keyword IS NOT NULL AND k.keyword IN ('fight',
'superhero',
'computer-animated-movie',
'blind-date')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2008
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi_idx.info < '8'
inner join info_type AS it2
on it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND it2.info = 'rating'
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Bulgaria',
'Germany',
'Danish',
'Norway',
'USA',
'English',
'Denmark',
'Swedish',
'Norwegian',
'USA')
inner join info_type AS it1
on it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it1.info = 'countries'
inner join kind_type AS kt
on kt.id = t.kind_id AND kt.kind IN ('movie',
'episode');
